/li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Occupational_therapist\" title=\"Occupational therapist\">Occupational therapist</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Safety_engineering\" title=\"Safety engineering\">Safety engineering</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_occupational_safety_and_health_agencies\" title=\"List of occupational safety and health agencies\">Agencies</a> and organizations</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;background:#F4F0EC\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Canadian_Centre_for_Occupational_Health_and_Safety\" title=\"Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety\">Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/European_Agency_for_Safety_and_Health_at_Work\" title=\"European Agency for Safety and Health at Work\">European Agency for Safety and Health at Work</a></li>\n<li>UK <a href=\"/wiki/Health_and_Safety_Executive\" title=\"Health and Safety Executive\">Health and Safety Executive</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/International_Labour_Organization\" title=\"International Labour Organization\">International Labour Organization</a></li>\n<li>U.S. <a href=\"/wiki/National_Institute_for_Occupational_Safety_and_Health\" title=\"National Institute for Occupational Safety and Health\">National Institute for Occupational Safety and Health</a></li>\n<li>U.S. <a href=\"/wiki/Occupational_Safety_and_Health_Administration\" title=\"Occupational Safety and Health Administration\">Occupational Safety and Health Administration</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/World_Health_Organization\" title=\"World Health Organization\">World Health Organization</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Standards</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-wi